  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/c1ab3484c2cd93fcc9a37137e8df5467.poster.avif?t=1764148328\" width=800 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/c1ab3484c2cd93fcc9a37137e8df5467.webm?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/c1ab3484c2cd93fcc9a37137e8df5467.mp4?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LiDAR Exploration Program</strong> is an atmospheric adventure game with light horror elements, where you can't see the world around you. Use the lidar scanner to colorize everything around you. The game contains several levels to explore, in each of which you have to scan unknown objects. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE AND SCAN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/b5f918d9fb642da9954d57d54de6f546.poster.avif?t=1764148328\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/b5f918d9fb642da9954d57d54de6f546.webm?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/b5f918d9fb642da9954d57d54de6f546.mp4?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You find yourself in complete darkness, in which you can't see anything, but thanks to the scanner you can find your way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SCAN UNKNOWN OBJECTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/1a986cf6742be0775dc2216e9297bade.poster.avif?t=1764148328\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/1a986cf6742be0775dc2216e9297bade.webm?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/1a986cf6742be0775dc2216e9297bade.mp4?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You will have to look for objects, some of them will be ordinary, and some will seem very strange and creepy. Using the scanner you will be able to explore them.  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >USE MAP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/fe0bf334bede1cda836324779e009185.poster.avif?t=1764148328\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/fe0bf334bede1cda836324779e009185.webm?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/fe0bf334bede1cda836324779e009185.mp4?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You can use a map that shows the environment from above. With its help you can find the very objects that need to be scanned.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >8 LEVELS AVAILABLE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/b3c82b01e338e7ef9422664fb1c75783.poster.avif?t=1764148328\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/b3c82b01e338e7ef9422664fb1c75783.webm?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/b3c82b01e338e7ef9422664fb1c75783.mp4?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You have to explore 8 different locations in each of which you have to look for objects. You can explore the forest, cave, abandoned city and other locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quite simple and addictive gameplay, just walk and scan</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level has its own color palette, some objects have different colors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 levels available for exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customization of patterns for the scanner</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game was inspired by Scanner sombre and the G'mod Lidar addon. The game was originally created as a prototype called \"Lidar.exe\".</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/c1ab3484c2cd93fcc9a37137e8df5467.poster.avif?t=1764148328\" width=800 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/c1ab3484c2cd93fcc9a37137e8df5467.webm?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/c1ab3484c2cd93fcc9a37137e8df5467.mp4?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>LiDAR Exploration Program</strong> is an atmospheric adventure game with light horror elements, where you can't see the world around you. Use the lidar scanner to colorize everything around you. The game contains several levels to explore, in each of which you have to scan unknown objects. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORE AND SCAN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/b5f918d9fb642da9954d57d54de6f546.poster.avif?t=1764148328\" width=800 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/b5f918d9fb642da9954d57d54de6f546.webm?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/b5f918d9fb642da9954d57d54de6f546.mp4?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You find yourself in complete darkness, in which you can't see anything, but thanks to the scanner you can find your way.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SCAN UNKNOWN OBJECTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\