83.webm?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1882190/extras/b3c82b01e338e7ef9422664fb1c75783.mp4?t=1764148328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You have to explore 8 different locations in each of which you have to look for objects. You can explore the forest, cave, abandoned city and other locations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quite simple and addictive gameplay, just walk and scan</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level has its own color palette, some objects have different colors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 levels available for exploration</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Customization of patterns for the scanner</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game was inspired by Scanner sombre and the G'mod Lidar addon. The game was originally created as a prototype called \"Lidar.exe\".</p>",
